{"tid":193054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【聲稱無父幹】22歲大學生做老闆，賣六萬八蚊威士忌","createTime":"2017-04-09T04:51:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T05:34:40.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bfb8525900dcb4bfcf367d96cbd52fb3e110cb62","tid":193054,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T04:51:16.000Z","msg":"今年22歲的鄭立德（Aslan）是理工大學旅遊管理系四年級學生，但他同時有另一個身份，就是一間威士忌專門店的老闆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或許你會懷疑，一個學生究竟哪裏來資金，開設一間威士忌專門店呢？Aslan面對這問題，淡定地揮一揮手回答：「很多人也好奇，為甚麼我會有錢開這間店，他們都會問是否家人資助？不過，事實是這筆錢全部都是我用自己能力賺回來的，<span style=\"color: red;\">因為我家的經濟條件不是太好，大家都只是打工仔而已</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但要開一間威士忌專門店，閒閒哋都要三四十萬，這對於一個家境普通的學生來說，應該不是小數目，究竟用甚麼方法可以賺到這麼多錢呢？<br />\n<br />\n他說：「因為很多人不懂得找威士忌，<span style=\"color: red;\">我會幫手搜羅一些他們想要的威士忌，我就從中賺到一筆錢</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係信不信由你"},{"pid":"ada881db2a51e7ee7834c7ba869951826cb4c7a9","tid":193054,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T04:55:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"704feb1a0365732b0179212c23962effa165967b","tid":193054,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T04:56:54.000Z","msg":"因為很多人不懂得找屎忽，我會幫手搜羅一些他們想要的屎忽，我就從中賺到一筆錢。<br />\n<br />\n咁我就信"},{"pid":"72cc0b5271645d54a9d202fee201428564f0fbdb","tid":193054,"uid":37220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T04:57:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實如果咁多年都死慳死底加埋係咁parttime補習，儲到廿零三十個唔出奇</blockquote><br />\nYES 讀U個時見過有人儲到300k"},{"pid":"d5b4495d73e3ff58037e250e66ca2f173d22bd5f","tid":193054,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T05:03:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為很多人不懂得找屎忽，我會幫手搜羅一些他們想要的屎忽，我就從中賺到一筆錢。<br />\n<br />\n咁我就信</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00f7826dd7e7988c8bbe01e45c4bee54d7c2faf","tid":193054,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T05:05:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf529e632cee126df35bc5e95ccf25c5902e940e","tid":193054,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T05:08:13.000Z","msg":"條友year2就揸audi返學 應該冇父幹"},{"pid":"345c473c3d27066ff3c57136381a0719435a4313","tid":193054,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T05:12:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條友year2就揸audi返學 應該冇父幹</blockquote><br />\n蓋Ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0187be7b74566ac6528cd2fc5af1e0bf878284c","tid":193054,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T05:14:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>條友year2就揸audi返學 應該冇父幹</blockquote><br />\n蓋Ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf27b04d69beab4e79efb53f019415f9653db2e","tid":193054,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T05:21:14.000Z","msg":"吳天海<br />\n霍建寧<br />\n<br />\n都係打工仔咋"},{"pid":"d8e5c4ff62a71ab410035858063af9b206f0abec","tid":193054,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T05:25:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吳天海<br />\n霍建寧<br />\n<br />\n都係打工仔咋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以篇報導我特登有紅色黎quote"},{"pid":"2d5ec049bbd48c305bc4920fde86d0162a195d38","tid":193054,"uid":28432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T05:34:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}